[
    {
        "content": "<p>I'm trying to learn proving in Lean4 by following \"The mechanics of proof\" and I have some questions about a proof:<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/hrmacbeth/math2001/blob/main/Math2001/02_Proofs_with_Structure/04_And.lean#L48\">https://github.com/hrmacbeth/math2001/blob/main/Math2001/02_Proofs_with_Structure/04_And.lean#L48</a></p>\n<p>We want to show that <code>a^2 + b^2 = 0</code> implies <code>a = 0</code> and <code>b = 0</code>:<br>\nPart of it is given, that <code>a^2 = 0</code>. I also managed to prove that <code>b^2 = 0</code>.</p>\n<p>The book (<a href=\"https://hrmacbeth.github.io/math2001/02_Proofs_with_Structure.html#id27\">https://hrmacbeth.github.io/math2001/02_Proofs_with_Structure.html#id27</a>) recommends to use the <code>cancel</code> tactic to derive that <code>a = 0</code>. However, we cannot cancel a, because it is zero?</p>\n<p>On a different note, I found the <code>pow_eq_zero_iff</code> lemma and I tried to use that:<br>\nThe relevant part of my proof state is</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ℝ</span>\n<span class=\"n\">h2</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"bp\">^</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">⊢</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Why does <code>apply pow_eq_zero_iff on h2</code> fail? I guess I got the syntax wrong but I don't even know what to google :(</p>\n<p>Full proof so far (might use tactics from the book that are not in mainstream Lean)</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ℝ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h1</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"bp\">^</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">+</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span> <span class=\"bp\">^</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span> <span class=\"bp\">∧</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">have</span> <span class=\"n\">h2</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"bp\">^</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">·</span> <span class=\"n\">apply</span> <span class=\"n\">le_antisymm</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">calc</span>\n      <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"bp\">^</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">≤</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"bp\">^</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">+</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span> <span class=\"bp\">^</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">extra</span>\n      <span class=\"n\">_</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">rw</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">h1</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">extra</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">have</span> <span class=\"n\">hb</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span> <span class=\"bp\">^</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">addarith</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">h1</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">h2</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">constructor</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">-- apply pow_eq_zero_iff on h2</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 401025366,
        "sender_full_name": "Philipp",
        "timestamp": 1699478569
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><code>on</code> is not a part of the syntax of <code>apply</code>, so that's definitely an issue</p>",
        "id": 401027859,
        "sender_full_name": "Ruben Van de Velde",
        "timestamp": 1699479718
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>And given that the theorem name ends with <code>_iff</code>, you'd be better off trying to use <code>rw [] at h2</code></p>",
        "id": 401028032,
        "sender_full_name": "Ruben Van de Velde",
        "timestamp": 1699479789
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Ah right. <code>apply pow_eq_zero_iff at h2</code> also fails though, why is that?</p>",
        "id": 401032141,
        "sender_full_name": "Philipp",
        "timestamp": 1699481617
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>This syntax simply does not exist.</p>",
        "id": 401033679,
        "sender_full_name": "Patrick Massot",
        "timestamp": 1699482403
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It will come actually, but not in the version of Mathlib used in this book now. But this won't help since <code>pow_eq_zero_iff</code> is a iff, not an implication.</p>",
        "id": 401033742,
        "sender_full_name": "Patrick Massot",
        "timestamp": 1699482446
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>You probably want to write <code>rw [pow_eq_zero_iff] at h2</code>.</p>",
        "id": 401033754,
        "sender_full_name": "Patrick Massot",
        "timestamp": 1699482457
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"638732\">Philipp</span> has marked this topic as resolved.</p>",
        "id": 401039100,
        "sender_full_name": "Notification Bot",
        "timestamp": 1699485473
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"638732\">@Philipp</span> Hi! The <code>cancel</code> tactic was written just for the course, which is why no one on Zulip has heard of it. (Eventually I would like to write a more robust version for mathlib.) The syntax in your example should be <code>cancel 2 at h2</code>.</p>",
        "id": 401105631,
        "sender_full_name": "Heather Macbeth",
        "timestamp": 1699519651
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"638732\">Philipp</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/113489-new-members/topic/.E2.9C.94.20The.20mechanics.20of.20proof.3A.20cancel.20tactic.20on.20a.5E2.20.3F/near/401032141\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Ah right. <code>apply pow_eq_zero_iff at h2</code> also fails though, why is that?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>This syntax is now being used in NNG4, so hopefully it will come to mathlib sooner rather than later</p>",
        "id": 401107001,
        "sender_full_name": "Mauricio Collares",
        "timestamp": 1699520107
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>But in NNG you can't apply an iff either, you can only apply an -&gt;</p>",
        "id": 401108952,
        "sender_full_name": "Kevin Buzzard",
        "timestamp": 1699520558
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Oh wow hi <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"260507\">@Heather Macbeth</span> ! :D Thank you so much for the book, I really enjoy working through it so far.<br>\nCould you explain what \"cancel 2 at ha\" means in natural language? I thought that <code>cancel x</code> meant \"divide both sides by x\" (but I just saw that Example 2.1.5 also uses <code>cancel 2 at</code>). So is it more a \"remove x from the equation if you can\" ?</p>",
        "id": 401219338,
        "sender_full_name": "Philipp",
        "timestamp": 1699556812
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"638732\">@Philipp</span> At the moment the tactic uses the <code>cancel 2 at h</code> syntax for a variety of different operations:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>simplify <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">2x=2y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8389em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span> to <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x=y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li>simplify <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">2x&lt;2y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6835em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8389em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span> to <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x&lt;y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.5782em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li>simplify <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x^2=y^2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.0085em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> to <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x=y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li>simplify <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0&lt;2x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6835em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span> to <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0&lt;x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6835em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li>simplify <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x^2=0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span> to <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x=0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>etc etc, with the uniting principle that in each of the above cases the 2 is \"being removed\".  But perhaps these different simplifications are not closely enough related to make it a good syntax.</p>\n<p>(Another consideration: when rewriting it for mathlib I'd also like it to be able to, e.g., simplify <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>log</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>log</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\log x = \\log y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">lo<span style=\"margin-right:0.01389em;\">g</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">lo<span style=\"margin-right:0.01389em;\">g</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span> to <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x=y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span>.  But what would be the syntax for that?  <code>cancel log at h</code>?)</p>",
        "id": 401470618,
        "sender_full_name": "Heather Macbeth",
        "timestamp": 1699673365
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>One alternative syntax I have been thinking about would be a pattern syntax (these are currently used in <code>congrm</code>, <code>gcongr</code>, <code>linear_combination</code>, ...) something like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>cancel 2 * ?_ at h</code> can mean<ul>\n<li>simplify <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">2x=2y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8389em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span> to <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x=y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li>simplify <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">2x&lt;2y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6835em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8389em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span> to <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x&lt;y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.5782em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li>simplify <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0&lt;2x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6835em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span> to <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0&lt;x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6835em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li>...</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>cancel ?_ ^ 2 at h</code> can mean<ul>\n<li>simplify <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x^2=y^2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.0085em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> to <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x=y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li>simplify <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x^2=0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span> to <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x=0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li>...</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>cancel log ?_ at h</code> can mean<ul>\n<li>simplify <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>log</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>log</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\log x = \\log y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">lo<span style=\"margin-right:0.01389em;\">g</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">lo<span style=\"margin-right:0.01389em;\">g</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span> to <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x=y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li>...</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>I'm not sure whether (particularly for my target audience of undergrads and other newbies) this is clearer or less clear.</p>",
