    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"260507\">@Heather Macbeth</span>  I (as a newbie) like that alternative syntax :)<br>\nIt comes closer to the</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">^</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span> <span class=\"bp\">^</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span>  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">sqrt</span>\n<span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>or</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span>  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">div</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n<span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>style for solving equations that I learned in highschool.</p>\n<p>However, I'm a Software Engineer (with an M.Sc. in computer science), so I don't know if that's also helpful for your target audience.</p>",
        "id": 401504795,
        "sender_full_name": "Philipp",
        "timestamp": 1699702990
    }
